Sentencas: Thermochemical gasification of biomass through the supercritical water gasification (SCWG) has high gasification efficiency at lower temperatures and can deal directly with wet biomass without drying.
Titulo: Performance of a Ni/Al2O3 cermet-supported tubular solid oxide fuel cell operating with biomass-based syngas through supercritical water

Sentencas: Besides, solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) appear to be an important technology in the future as they can operate at a high efficiency.
Titulo: Performance of a Ni/Al2O3 cermet-supported tubular solid oxide fuel cell operating with biomass-based syngas through supercritical water

Sentencas: Therefore, the combination of biomass gasification through supercritical water with SOFC represents one of the most potential applications for highly efficient utilization of biomass.
